Dear Investors,

We are pleased to announce that the deal trend at Liquidity Capital II, L.P=
. (=93the Fund=94) is increasing.

The growing trend is attributed to various factors, including: the manageme=
nt company=92s ongoing investment in marketing, additional members in our s=
ales team, brand awareness in the marketplace and an increase in demand as =
growth in many hi-tech companies has accelerated.

Over the past three months, the Fund has signed 9 new transactions, committ=
ing to transfer funds totaling $67.3 million. Bringing the total transactio=
ns signed to 25 since the Fund=92s inception, and approximately $346.4 mill=
ion in commitments.

In addition, the deployment rate of funds to companies has increased. In th=
e past quarter, the Fund transferred $13 million, bringing the total funds =
transferred to companies to circa $85.7 million.

As of September 30, 2021, total loans committed by the Fund, stands at $56.=
5 million, and the cash balance is circa $4.7 million.

To meet these needs and enable deployments, on September 29th, 2021, we hel=
d a 15% commitment Capital Call. This brought the Fund to call 100% of the =
Investors=92 commitment.

Additionally, in accordance with the Fund=92s agreement, the external distr=
ibution originally scheduled to take place this month (about $3.1 million i=
n total) will be postponed, and the investment=92s funds will be reinvested=
 in the companies, in order to maximize the investors=92 returns.

The Fund=92s team continues to be committed to your best interests, in look=
ing for impressive future investment opportunities.



Kind Regards,
